10 "§ 75-156. Contracts void.
11 Contracts for debt adjusting or debt settlement are void as against public policy.
12 "§ 75-157. Unfair trade practice.
13 A violation of this Article is an unfair trade practice under G.S. 75-1.1."
14 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025, and applies to offenses
15 committed on or after that date.
